                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/14144.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Special
                        Agent <persName type="to">Carothers</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-01-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 7, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Yours January 5. Will call War Department’s attention to your recommendation that
                    General Scott be permitted to call upon villa freely in Juarez. Approve your
                    recommendation that Villa be permitted to come to El Paso for consultation.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
